  "title": "Full-Time Cafe Service Crew",
  "description": "<h3>Our cafe located in Joo Chiat is hiring!!</h3>\n<h3>(5 day work week, 44 hrs shift per week)</h3>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>• Greet customers with a friendly attitude.</p>\n<p>• Take orders and handle cashier duties.</p>\n<p>• Ensure accurate data entry in the POS system.</p>\n<p>• Prepare and serve food and beverages according to customer orders.</p>\n<p>• Maintain shop cleanliness and follow food hygiene standards.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Previous experience will be an added advantage.</p>\n<p>· Ability to work in a fast-paced environment.</p>\n<p>· Good communication and teamwork skills.</p>\n<p>· Food hygiene certificate preferred.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p>· 5 day work week</p>\n<p>· Staff meal provided</p>\n<p>· Staff Discount</p>\n<p>· Birthday Leave</p>\n<p>· Medical and Dental Benefits</p>\n<p>· Monthly Store Performance Incentive</p>\n<p>· Variable Allowances</p>\n<p>· Bi-Annual Bonus</p>\n<p>· Training and Uniform provided</p>\n<p>· Skill development and career progression opportunities</p>\n<p>· $1200 New Join Bonus Incentive (T&amp;C Applies)</p>",
